title: 150PCS Life Story Interview Kit Cards - Tales Life Story Interview Kit, Get to Know Grandparents and Parents for Family Game Night with Curated Question Cards
features: 【150 Life Story Interview Kit Cards】Get to know your grandparents or great-grandparents! Hear them talk about their lives! 150 gentle conversation starters to help guide your grandparent or parent through the memories of their rich and interesting life. A careful balance of specific and open-ended questions help them talk about their lives from childhood to adulthood, relationships, genealogy, and the good old days!

【Capture Life Stories】Capture your loved one's life story,your loved ones' stories and memories for generations to come.Deepen your connection with them Spend learning more about and connecting with the people that love you most.

【Build Friendships with Parents】Enjoy easy conversation as friends without the awkward, uncomfortable generational boundaries! Create lasting bonds while sharing memories and making new ones as you work through the game deck. The gift for parents who have everything is a deep and meaningful relationship

【Excellent Craftsmanship】Made from high-quality materials, our conversation cards offer a stimulating and engaging way to connect with others. With durable, environmentally friendly cardboards and fine workmanship, the high-definition color printing brings the cards to life.

【Conversation Starter Cards】The right questions at the right time,150 questions written by our team of interviewers and trained narratologists,Mixture of chronological and reflective questions that spark meaningful conversations,Divided into three eras of life: Early Life, Mid Life, and Later Life & Reflection
